title: Music Recording Studios in the Borough of Manhattan, 2007
name: Music Recording Studios in the Borough of Manhattan, 2007
description:
A geocoded of recording studios in Manhattan. Get inspired by the surroundings and channel you inner Coltrane, Sinatra, Dee Dee or H.O.V.A. There are over 200 studios on the island of Manhattan alone. This data was compiled from business listings in the Yellow Pages under the heading 'recording studios'.
